    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter to make compline about customer service that I received my QNB city centre branch lately. Although the chequebook was requested around 15 days back, I have not received any proper response from the bank as of now.",
        "Two weeks ago, I ordered a chequebook by filling the form and customer service argent, while I visited the abovesaid branch. But neither have I received the chequebook nor any correspondence from the bank regarding my request. I urgently require a new chequebook as It is required to give a post-dated cheque while I am signing a new house rental agreement by next week. I maintain the current account in the abovementioned branch and my account no is no 099910933131",
        "I am requesting a proper explanation for the delay and poor services. Please inform me how long I have to wait for my chequebook and I would like to know what action you are going to do?",
